Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.28,0:22:31.83,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,mi mi miracle…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.16,0:22:31.22,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}（已经擅自开始了啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:33.55,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}（诶？）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.91,0:22:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晴天晴天是也
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.94,0:22:39.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那摄像机真强大…
