Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.18,0:22:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.21,0:22:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暂且就唱「恋之稔传说」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.24,0:22:47.30,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（暂且？#）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.33,0:22:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么接下来就…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.25,0:22:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自我发挥就好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:03.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.66,0:23:05.80,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（OK了么？）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.80,0:23:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自我发挥
